headline: CallMiner Announces 2025 LISTEN Award Winners, Recognizing Achievements in Customer Experience, Automation, and Conversation Intelligence
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., November 04, 2025--CallMiner, the global leader in AI-powered conversation intelligence and customer experience (CX) automation, announced the winners of the 2025 LISTEN Awards at its annual user conference, LISTEN 2025. The CallMiner LISTEN Awards honor customers and partners for their use of CallMiner’s CX automation platform, driving improvements across CX, contact center efficiency, agent performance, and more.
